wikipedia_page.main: Ralph Millington (18 June 1930 – December 1999) was an English footballer who played as centre half for Neston, Tranmere Rovers and Ellesmere Port. He made 381 appearances for Tranmere, of which 357 were in the English Football League.

response: * Ralph Millington (1930 in Neston – 1999) an English footballer who played 357 games for Tranmere Rovers F.C.
